@startuml
title Process Sale State Diagram

[*] --> WaitingForSale

state WaitingForSale
state AddingItems
state PaymentVerification
state PaymentCompleted
state SaleCompleted
[*]

WaitingForSale --> AddingItems : new sale

AddingItems --> Payment : all items added

Payment --> PaymentVerification : pay by card or check
AddingItems --> PaymentCompleted : pay by cash

PaymentVerification --> PaymentCompleted : payment approved

PaymentCompleted --> WaitingForSale : sale finished

@enduml
